><p> Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen 今年早些时候宣布携复出单曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemen-share-comeback-single-showtime-and-announce-more-uk-headline-shows-3591486">Showtime</a> 》回归，乐队此前曾在二月份在其社交媒体频道上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-post-clip-of-first-new-music-in-five-years-3589012">发布了一段 6 秒的曲目片段来调侃这</a>首歌曲。乐队还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemen-announce-7-inch-and-merch-for-new-single-showtime-back-to-the-graft-again-3590146">发布了预购的 7 英寸白色黑胶唱片《Showtime》以及新商品</a>。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemen-release-rare-bonus-track-asa-from-the-balcony-10th-anniversary-reissue-3776175">乐队分享了即将发行的《The Balcony》十周年纪念版的附赠曲目《ASA》。</a>该曲目最初于 2013 年作为《Rango》的 B 面发行。</p><p>他们目前正在准备纪念他们开创性的首张专辑发行十周年。再版将于 9 月 16 日发售 - 请<a href="https://catb.lnk.to/TB10collectionWE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订。</p><p>除了《ASA》之外，《The Balcony》及其十周年再版也将收录<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-22-1222666">Ewan McGregor 翻唱的《Hourglass》</a> 、《Rango》（单曲版）和其他三首额外曲目。 </p><figure id="attachment_3027264" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3027264" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3027264" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/CatfishBottlemen-news.jpg" alt="鲶鱼" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/CatfishBottlemen-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/CatfishBottlemen-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/CatfishBottlemen-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/CatfishBottlemen-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/CatfishBottlemen-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/CatfishBottlemen-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3027264" class="wp-caption-text"> Van McCann 与 Catfish And The Bottlemen 一起现场表演。图片来源：盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>此外，还将推出限量版7英寸单曲盒装，仅限购买2,000张。</p><p>他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-announce-first-sadium-shows-in-england-and-wales-for-summer-2025-3784801">还宣布了他们的首次体育场巡演</a>，将于 2025 年 8 月开始。门票现已发售，您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fcatfish-and-the-bottlemen-tickets%2Fartist%2F5121447" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买。本周早些时候，粉丝们对“Cocoon”热门制作人将在绿洲乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">将在温布利球场举行重聚演出的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-to-catfish-the-bottlemens-london-stadium-show-now-falling-on-the-same-day-as-oasis-3787934">同一天接管伦敦托特纳姆热刺体育场的消息做出反应</a>。</p><p>鲶鱼和装瓶工<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/catfish-the-bottlemen-reading-festival-2024-review-setlist-photos-3787168">成为今年雷丁和利兹音乐节的头条新闻</a>。 <em>《NME》</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/catfish-the-bottlemen-reading-festival-2024-review-setlist-photos-3787168">对他们的表现进行四星评价时</a>表示：“他们知道自己的前进方向。其中有一段“The Bartender And The Thief”的片段，厚颜无耻地向他们的同胞<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stereophonics">Stereophonics</a>致敬，而“2all”的聚光灯和戏剧表演则表明他们已经在大空间中迈出了步伐。</p><p> “《Outside》的宽银幕精神错乱和崩溃甚至带有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/PINK-FLOYD">平克·弗洛伊德</a>的味道。他们的演奏比上次更加令人着迷，他们当然知道一支伟大的乐队应该看起来、听起来和感觉是什么样的。我们面前的人群欣喜若狂。它们会繁殖以填补这些空间吗？也许长远的尝试会得到回报。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemen-cancel-dublin-gig-shortly-before-doors-are-due-to-open-3789472">《Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen》在开幕前不久取消了都柏林演出的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
神秘人取消所有即将到来的巡演日期https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-mysterines-cancel-all-upcoming-tour-dates-3789447?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-mysterines-cancel-all-upcoming-tour-datesLaura Molloy Sat, 31 Aug 2024 19:51:38 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music NewsRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3789447 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《神秘人》中的莉亚·梅特卡夫。图片来源：吉姆·戴森/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们向所有期待看到我们表演的人致以诚挚的歉意，对于由此造成的失望，我们深表歉意。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-mysterines-cancel-all-upcoming-tour-dates-3789447">《The Mysterines》取消所有即将举行的巡演日期的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《神秘人》中的莉亚·梅特卡夫。图片来源：吉姆·戴森/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Lia-Metcalfe-of-The-Mysterines.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-mysterines">神秘乐队</a>取消了即将到来的英国和欧盟巡演。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-mysterines-live-in-liverpool-radar-3197612">神秘人住在利物浦：家乡英雄的喧闹回归</a></strong></li></ul><p>这支利物浦垃圾摇滚四人乐队原定于 10 月 18 日在都柏林举办一系列秋季演出。然而，今天（8 月 31 日）他们宣布取消演出日期。</p><p>在分享给 Instagram 的一份声明中，乐队告诉粉丝，“由于最近的情况”，他们“心情沉重”地取消了所有计划的巡演日期。目前尚不清楚具体情况如何。</p><p>他们说：“我们非常高兴与你们分享这次旅行，但经过仔细考虑，我们决定这不是我们目前最好的决定。” “我们向所有期待看到我们表演的人致以诚挚的歉意，对于由此造成的失望，我们深表歉意。”</p><p> “请知道，您的支持对我们来说意味着整个世界，”他们继续说道。 “感谢您这段时间的理解和耐心。”</p><p>门票可在购买时退款。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_VyU0gNG_E/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-conten